SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT CO_ID,BR_ID,FISCAL_YEAR,PERIOD_NO,JOURNAL_DT,JOURNAL_NO,GL_JURNALH.JOURNAL_ID,CURR_ID,CURR_RATE,REF_NO,KET_HD ,F_REVERSE,REVERSE_NO,DEBIT_AMT,CREDIT_AMT,DEBIT_HOME,CREDIT_HOME, USER_UPD,DATE_UPD,IIF(STATUS='V',USER_VOID,USER_POST) ST_USER,IIF(STATUS='V',DATE_VOID,DATE_POST) ST_DATE, STATUS,APPL_ID,F_APPROVED,KET FROM GL_JURNALH (NOLOCK) left join CM_HTRXKB (NOLOCK) on coid=co_id and CM_HTRXKB.JOURNAL_ID=GL_JURNALH.JOURNAL_ID WHERE CO_ID=':1' AND BR_ID=':2' AND FISCAL_YEAR=:3 AND PERIOD_NO=:4 AND GL_JURNALH.JOURNAL_ID=:5 AND upper(ISNULL(REF_NO,'')) LIKE '%:6%' AND upper(ISNULL(KET_HD,'')) LIKE '%:7%' :8
